        "caption": ""
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Eventually, this led Shelby American to visit the school alongside Scott Black, who gave a presentation about his personal hero Carroll Shelby. After reminiscing on the life of the automotive legend, the team took the kids outside to look at a genuine ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "children": [
              {
                "detail": 0,
                "format": 0,
                "mode": "normal",
                "style": "",
                "text": "Shelby Cobra",
                "type": "text",
                "version": 1
              }
            ],
            "direction": "ltr",
            "format": "",
            "indent": 0,
            "type": "link",
            "rel": null,
            "target": null,
            "title": null,
            "url": "__GHOST_URL__/articles/features-3/ten-things-shelby-cobra/",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": ". While other kids watched in awe of the car's excellence, Jacob was able to ride shotgun with Black at the helm through the neighborhood surrounding the area. Reportedly, Jacob described the experience as the \"best school day ever,\" and we certainly must agree with that.",
